'''DWVN-TV''' channel 45, is a [[television station]] of [[Gateway UHF Broadcasting]]. The station is an affiliate of [[3ABN|Three Angels Broadcasting Network]], a U.S.-based religious [[television network]] associated with the [[Seventh-day Adventist Church]]. Its Manila transmitter is located at Sumulong Highway, Block 5, Brgy. Sta. Cruz, [[Antipolo City]], Rizal Province.
